          h1 Agriculture &amp; Water Technology Development Hub
          p.subheadtext iHub - AWaDH is an initiative of the Department of Science & Technology, Government of India, in the framework of National Mission on Interdisciplinary Cyber - Physical Systems at the Indian Institute of Technology Ropar.
        
